# Phase scope and build guardrails

## Current phase: 6 (complete)

Consumable git pin tag `v0.1.0`. Run `./scripts/verify-release.sh` before any new release tag.

## Build guardrails

1. `export CARGO_BUILD_JOBS=1` on constrained hosts.
2. `export CARGO_TARGET_DIR=target-spectra-extract` (or `target-spectra-e2e`, `target-spectra-bench`).
3. Scope narrowly: `-p uf-spectra-core` / `-p uf-spectra-core` path, `-p spectra-e2e`, etc. Facade package is `uf-spectra` (lib `spectra`).
4. One cargo command at a time on shared dev machines.
5. Never run parallel heavy `cargo` builds on disk-constrained WSL hosts.

## Read order

README → per-crate README → `cargo doc -p uf-spectra` for the task scope.
